SIMPLE: kneed
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Kneed
<hw>Kneed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Having
knees;- used chiefly in composition; <as>as, in-<ex>kneed</ex>;
out-<ex>kneed</ex>; weak-<ex>kneed</ex>.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Geniculated; forming an obtuse
angle at the joints, like the knee when a little bent; <as>as,
<ex>kneed</ex> grass</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Knee-deep</ent>⟦br⟧
